 head like a pigeon in order to move around and interact with your world\n\u2022 Unlock and discover four different levels\n\u2022 Protect your bread from other pigeons\n\u2022 Use power-ups and map shortcuts to be faster than other pigeons\n\u2022 Your pigeon enemies come in different shapes, avoid unnecessary conflicts!", "short_description": "All the world\u2019s a rooftop, and all the men and women merely pigeons. \n\nUse the power of VR and absolutely unique movement controls to slip into your pigeon-self!\nGo out into the world and find a rooftop. Wait for the granny to throw some bread. Eat as much bread as possible! BREAD IS LIFE!"}]}, "developer_name": "Maestro Pivetta", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrkiwi.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/VR-Pigeons-EULA.pdf", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VRKiwi (Mekiwi)", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vrkiwi.org/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "CASUAL", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "719676208998706"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 5, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1023333545958392"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1622766858280561"}, {"status": "CANCELLED", "id": "1043611793342018"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "525170169172969"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "203430668352776"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "525170169172969"}, "is_approved": true, "first